    {
        "content": "<p>Do you think <code>nhds_right a</code> should be defined as <code>nhds_within (Ioi a)</code> or <code>nhds_within (Ici a)</code> ? e.g do we want <code>tendsto (Œª x : ‚Ñù, 1/x) (nhds_right 0) at_top</code> to be true ?</p>",
