        "sender_full_name": "Patrick Massot",
        "timestamp": 1596049604
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>We can have notation both for <code>nhds_within (Ioi a) a</code> and <code>nhds_within (Ici a) a</code>. Both are useful.</p>",
